_struct_biol.id        1 
_struct_biol.details   
;The structure is of a domain-swapped dimer.  The domain swap 
occurs at VAL 69.  To generate the biological unit, it is necessary to 
pair residues 21-68 from Chain A with 69-84 of Chain B, residues 21-68 
from Chain B with 69-84 of Chain A, residues 20-68 of Chain C with 69-84 
of Chain D, and 20-68 of Chain D with 69-84 of Chain C.
;
